absolutely disgusting.

00:38.667 --> 00:42.667 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: And
remembering George
Michael, the '80s pop star
and gay rights advocate

00:43.433 --> 00:45.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
