that they have suspended working
ties with 12 of the nations

01:12.233 --> 01:14.167 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that backed the resolution.

01:14.167 --> 01:17.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Prime Minister Benjamin
Netanyahu will not meet with
their foreign ministers, and the

01:17.600 --> 01:21.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Israeli foreign minister will
not receive their ambassadors.

01:21.033 --> 01:25.767 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Meanwhile, president-elect Trump
again tweeted his own criticism
of the United Nations this

01:25.767 --> 01:27.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
evening.

01:27.733 --> 01:30.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
