rising tensions on a Greek
island that's welcomed
thousands of refugees;

04:08.700 --> 04:12.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a deadly Christmas weekend
in Chicago; and much more.

04:23.167 --> 04:26.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
