see where the policies are.

08:12.833 --> 08:14.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: Right.

08:14.333 --> 08:15.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: We know
where the opinions are.

08:15.600 --> 08:17.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Maybe the policies will
or will not follow that.

08:17.700 --> 08:20.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Let's talk a
little bit now about the whole
conflict of interest issue.

08:20.200 --> 08:24.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
