08:33.167 --> 08:35.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: Well, it's
a start, but I don't think
it will be the finish or is

08:35.900 --> 08:39.667 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the finish, and I don't think
