about foreign policy,
and relationships,
and economic issues.

08:52.500 --> 08:54.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I just don't see it.

08:54.033 --> 08:56.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, is this a first step,
a significant first step?

08:56.733 --> 08:58.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I guess so.

08:58.833 --> 09:02.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
