problem, which is he's got a
lot of interests around the

09:06.233 --> 09:07.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
world.

09:07.600 --> 09:09.267 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Yes, I
absolutely agree with that.

09:09.267 --> 09:11.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
