another political
headache off the table.

09:11.833 --> 09:16.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Remember throughout the
campaign, The Washington
Post had been reporting
on a lot of issues

09:18.833 --> 09:21.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with that foundation, where
it was getting its money, what
it was and wasn't doing with

09:21.333 --> 09:23.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

09:23.333 --> 09:25.967 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There is an actual open
investigation by the New
York state attorney general.

