urban affairs at Northeastern

29:44.833 --> 29:47.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Illinois University and an
inner-city youth advocate.

29:47.900 --> 29:49.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LANCE WILLIAMS: This is not
a law enforcement problem.

29:49.800 --> 29:52.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
