They need a cultural
retooling process.

30:03.333 --> 30:08.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Williams says it's a
culture that's developed in the
absence of working institutions

30:08.167 --> 30:11.067 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and in the midst of
crushing poverty.

30:11.067 --> 30:14.467 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
One big cause of
much frustration?

30:14.467 --> 30:19.467 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Nearly half of black men in
