rate of 32 percent.

30:24.367 --> 30:26.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
LANCE WILLIAMS:
There's a lot of rage.

30:26.500 --> 30:28.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
There's a lot of anger.

30:28.833 --> 30:31.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
