same forms of depression.

30:52.367 --> 30:57.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Another
structural factor playing
into the violence, Chicago
is one of the nation's

30:57.867 --> 30:59.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
