JOHN YANG: ... you got
your bachelor's degree.

31:56.133 --> 31:57.367 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHICO TILLMON: Yes, sir.

31:57.367 --> 31:58.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JOHN YANG: You got
your master's degree.

31:58.200 --> 31:59.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHICO TILLMON: Yes, sir.

31:59.433 --> 32:00.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JOHN YANG: You're
working on your Ph.D.

32:00.333 --> 32:01.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHICO TILLMON: Yes, sir.

32:01.833 --> 32:03.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: How long, how many
years are we talking about here?

32:03.100 --> 32:04.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CHICO TILLMON: Five years.

32:04.100 --> 32:05.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Pretty determined.

32:05.100 --> 32:06.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHICO TILLMON: Yes.

32:06.133 --> 32:07.500 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Pretty motivated.

32:07.500 --> 32:09.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHICO TILLMON: Yes, sir.

32:09.567 --> 32:13.867 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
