of 75th and Stewart, Tamar
Manasseh is also determined

32:27.500 --> 32:29.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
that change will happen.

32:29.567 --> 32:33.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMAR MANASSEH: It's going to
take a lot of people all doing
something, not saying something,

32:34.567 --> 32:36.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
