by the same things.

32:46.800 --> 32:50.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, sometimes, when we don't
talk to each other, when we
don't interact, we miss that.

32:50.900 --> 32:55.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: On one
corner, a small effort in
response to a big problem.

