Fans today are mourning the loss
of singer and musician George
Michael and paying tribute

33:38.300 --> 33:42.167 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to him as one of pop's biggest
stars of the '80s and '90s.

33:42.167 --> 33:45.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Michael shot to fame as a
member of the duo Wham! and then
launched a hugely successful

33:45.933 --> 33:47.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
solo career.

33:47.933 --> 33:51.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
His friend Elton John called
him -- quote - - "the kindest,
most generous soul and a

33:51.400 --> 33:53.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
brilliant artist."

33:53.300 --> 33:56.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, for all of his
success, Michael faced
personal struggles as well.

33:56.500 --> 34:00.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He died on Christmas Day
at his home in Oxfordshire,
England, at the age of 53.

34:00.200 --> 34:02.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Let's begin with this
remembrance by Angus Walker of
Independent Television News.

34:02.833 --> 34:03.767 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGUS WALKER: His songs,
his voice, his stunning
success, George Michael,
singer, writer, producer,

34:03.767 --> 34:05.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
perhaps the perfect pop star.

34:05.733 --> 34:07.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Just 21, he wrote Wham!'s
breakthrough single, topping
the charts in the U.K. and U.S.

34:07.233 --> 34:08.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He and Andrew Ridgeley had
met at school near Watford.

34:08.733 --> 34:09.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Their brand of bouncy pop
was carefree, colorful.

34:09.933 --> 34:11.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Wham! soon sold more
than 25 million records.

34:11.967 --> 34:14.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
World-famous, their crafty
manager secured a 1985 tour
to China, the first glimpse of

34:14.000 --> 34:16.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Western pop culture for
a country emerging from a
brutal cultural revolution.

34:16.067 --> 34:17.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
His solo career began
with another number
one hit, new image, new
fans, multiple awards,

34:17.967 --> 34:19.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
100 million records sold,
making him one of bestselling
artists of all time.

34:19.400 --> 34:21.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But it wasn't just his
music attracting attention.

34:21.433 --> 34:23.467 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
