34:26.133 --> 34:27.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GEORGE MICHAEL, Musician: I
have been doing this on and
off since I was a teenager, and

34:27.067 --> 34:28.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
never once seen violence.

34:28.300 --> 34:29.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
