lied about my sex life.

34:29.533 --> 34:31.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ANGUS WALKER: He also
admitted heavy drug use.

34:31.600 --> 34:32.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Arrested after crashing his car
while intoxicated near his North
London home, he was sent to

34:32.400 --> 34:34.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
