34:34.967 --> 34:36.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Five years ago, he came
close to death, spending
10 days in hospital,
suffering from pneumonia.

34:36.133 --> 34:38.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
2016, another
superstar leaves us.

34:38.333 --> 34:39.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: One
of Michael's important
legacies over time was
how he eventually came

34:39.567 --> 34:41.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
