34:46.833 --> 34:48.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
TIM TEEMAN, The
Daily Beast: Yes.

34:48.833 --> 34:49.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: When you look
back at his career, where do
you put him in the pantheon

34:49.500 --> 34:51.133 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
