35:35.267 --> 35:37.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They are slow dances.

35:37.033 --> 35:38.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And they have remained.

35:38.633 --> 35:40.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And they have transcended.

35:40.700 --> 35:43.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If they were considered cheesy
-- and they were considered
slightly cheesy back in the

35:43.500 --> 35:45.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
